    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hard, dense, close-grained wood of the species Albizia lebbek of tropical Asia and Africa, having a dark brown color with gray streaks. Not truly a walnut. It is used for furniture, paneling, and in interior decorative work. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
